ost_discuss_num post_info_meta"><i class="icon_post_opr_view"></i>11</span></div></div><!----></li><li data-doc-id="000c8460d3c4081a286992b1b51800" data-title="分包报错pages***不应该在分包subPackages[x] 中？" data-create-time="1572484382" data-blog-category="1" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="post_item post_overview post_item_simple_qa"><h2 class="post_title"><!----><!----><a href="/community/develop/doc/000c8460d3c4081a286992b1b51800" class="" target="_blank">分包报错pages***不应该在分包subPackages[x] 中？</a><meta check-reduce="" itemprop="name" content="分包报错pages***不应该在分包subPackages[x] 中？"><meta check-reduce="" itemprop="url" content="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/community/develop/doc/000c8460d3c4081a286992b1b51800"></h2><!----><p class="post_desc">有些分包的目录是右键page自动生成的，但是在pages中的路径已经删了，还是报错，检查了几遍发现好像没写错，开发工具重启过，电脑也重启过，还是报错，基础库版本2.9.1，工具版本v1.02.1910120，目前用的测试ID    [图片]    </p><div class="post_tags_container"></div><div class="post_info"><!----><span class="post_group">[问答]</span><em class="post_time post_info_meta">28分钟前</em><div class="post_info_extend"><!----><span itemprop="commentCount" class="post_discuss_num post_info_meta"><i class="icon_post_opr_discuss"></i>0</span><span class="post_discuss_num post_info_meta"><i class="icon_post_opr_view"></i>18</span></div></div><!----></li><li data-doc-id="000a8edb91c340ea28691cd1253400" data-title="当微信支付异步通知时怎么验证签名？" data-create-time="1572484319" data-blog-category="1" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="post_item post_overview post_item_simple_qa"><h2 class="post_title"><!----><!----><a href="/community/develop/doc/000a8edb91c340ea28691cd1253400" class="" target="_blank">当微信支付异步通知时怎么验证签名？</a><meta check-reduce="" itemprop="name" content="当微信支付异步通知时怎么验证签名？"><meta check-reduce="" itemprop="url" content="https://developers.weixin.qq.com/community/develop/doc/000a8edb91c340ea28691cd1253400"></h2><!----><p class="post_desc">我想问一下，当微信支付异步通知通知我的时候，我按照官方的方法生成签名算法，怎么去判断这个签名有没有被篡改